lead_paragraph: Retired U.S. woman's soccer star Abby Wambach was arrested in Oregon on charges of driving under the influence of alcohol, an incident for which the popular player apologized on Sunday on social media.

headline.print_headline: U.S. Women's Soccer Star Wambach Arrested for DUI, Apologizes
